    {"rank": 3, "doc_id": "citigroup_2024", "modality": "pdf_page", "locator": {"page_number": 2}, "content": "...the ACL associated with the margin lending portfolio. For additional information on the results of operations of Wealth in 2024, see 'Wealth' below."},
