    {"rank": 5, "doc_id": "citigroup_2024", "modality": "pdf_page", "locator": {"page_number": 26}, "content": "WEALTH: Wealth includes the Private Bank, Wealth at Work and Citigold businesses. At Dec 31, 2024, Wealth had $313B in deposits, $587B in client investment assets and $148B in loans. Net new investment asset flows of $42B during 2024."},
